<event>
<main>true</main>
<tag>Sigma main event</tag>
<description>{CovLStrv2{The Docker Compose file sets the `no-new-privileges` attribute to `false` or omits it as the default value is `false`. This doesn't restrict the container from acquiring additional privileges via SUID or SGID bits. This allows privilege escalation, meaning a user can set the security context of the container and can perform root-level operations.}}</description>
<line>5</line>
</event>
<event>
<remediation>true</remediation>
<tag>remediation</tag>
<description>{CovLStrv2{Disable container privilege escalation by explicitly setting `no-new-privileges` to `true`.}}</description>
<line>5</line>
</event>
